:set rnu " Enable relative line numbering.
:syntax enable " Enables syntax highlighting.

:set expandtab " Pressing tab inserts 2 spaces.
:set tabstop=2 " Length of atb insertions is 2 spaces.
:set shiftwidth=2 " Auto inserted indentation is 2 spaces.

:set backspace=2 " Makes backspace work like most other apps.

:set lines=50 " Vim windows are 50 lines tall.
:set columns=100 " Vim windows are 100 columns wide.

:set smartindent " Automatically indent source while typing.
